<p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; justify-content: center; display: flex; flex-flow: row; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 90%; display: inline-block; width: 609.3px; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto; height: auto; border-style: solid; border-width: 2px; border-color: rgb(222, 78, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left; justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 35px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 606.1px; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.1429em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">为进一步深入学习习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想，推进理论学习走深走实，<span style="font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 30.0006px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">经济管理学院于<span style="font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 30.0006px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">12月29日</span>在A10-</span>402会议室召开党员大会。本次大会由<span style="font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 30.0006px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">经济管理学院党总支</span><span style="outline: 0px; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 30.0006px; cursor: text; text-align: left; caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">专职组织员周婷婷</span><span style="outline: 0px; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: text; text-indent: 2.1429em; caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">主持，学院党总支书记蔡平以及学生党支部全体党员参加此次会议。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.1429em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">此次大会的召开，主要<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 30.0006px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">讨论通过关于钟宝乐等3名同志由中共预备党员转为中共正式党员的问题，以及<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 30.0006px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">关于吸收吴本婷等3名同志由发展对象转为中共预备党员的问题。</span></span></span></p></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; line-height: 0; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 170px; height: auto; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><section draggable="true" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; line-height: 0; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; line-height: 0; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 170px; height: auto; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; line-height: 0; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></section><section style="margin: -10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; display: flex; flex-flow: row; text-align: center; justify-content: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: 25px; flex: 0 0 auto; align-self: center; height: auto;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 0;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; caret-color: red;">开展集中交流研讨</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; caret-color: red;"></strong></span></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; justify-content: center; display: flex; flex-flow: row; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 90%; display: inline-block; width: 609.3px; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto; height: auto; border-style: solid; border-width: 2px; border-color: rgb(222, 78, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left; justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 35px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 606.1px; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; z-index: 0; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section data-role="title" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="128867" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; z-index: 0; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px -8px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; z-index: 9; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 15px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(213, 58, 28); border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(255, 217, 82); letter-spacing: 1.5px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">奏唱国歌<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"/></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"></strong></span></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2664,894h-56V834h56l-27,30Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2608,890h53l4,4h-57v-4Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2632,884l-24,10V884h24Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; z-index: 0; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240109/1704791679436033004.jpg" title="1704791679436033004.jpg" alt="2.jpg" width="441" height="282" style="width: 441px; height: 282px;"/></p></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; z-index: 0; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; text-indent: 2.14285em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">活动伊始，由党总支书记蔡平<span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: text; caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important;">组织学生党支部全体党员同志奏唱国歌，全体人员原地肃立，激扬奋进的歌声鼓舞着现场的每一个人。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; text-indent: 2.14285em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><section data-role="title" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="128867" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; z-index: 0; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2385,894h56V834h-56l27,30Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2388,890h53v4h-57Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2417,884l24,10V884h-24Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path></svg></section></section><section style="margin: 0px -8px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; z-index: 9; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 15px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(213, 58, 28); border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(255, 217, 82); letter-spacing: 1.5px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">坚持“第一议题”<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"/></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"></strong></span></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2664,894h-56V834h56l-27,30Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2608,890h53l4,4h-57v-4Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2632,884l-24,10V884h24Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; text-indent: 2.14285em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: text; caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">随后由党总支书记蔡平组织学生党员学习《习近平总书记关于青年学生成长成才重要论述摘编》以及《习近平在文化传承发展座谈会上的讲话》。他表示必须深刻领会和全面把握习近平总书记从党和国家事业发展全局出发对广大青年提出的新要求、新希望，鼓励我院学生争做有理想、敢担当、能吃苦、肯奋斗的新时代好青年，坚持学习并弘扬中华优秀传统文化，坚定文化自信。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; text-indent: 2.14285em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><section data-role="title" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="128867" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; z-index: 0; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2385,894h56V834h-56l27,30Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2388,890h53v4h-57Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2417,884l24,10V884h-24Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path></svg></section></section><section style="margin: 0px -8px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; z-index: 9; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 15px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(213, 58, 28); border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(255, 217, 82); letter-spacing: 1.5px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">书记上党课<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"/></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"></strong></span></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2664,894h-56V834h56l-27,30Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2608,890h53l4,4h-57v-4Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2632,884l-24,10V884h24Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; text-indent: 2.14285em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240109/1704791742364010858.jpg" title="1704791742364010858.jpg" alt="3.jpg" width="509" height="344" style="width: 509px; height: 344px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; text-indent: 2.14285em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">他表示文化自信是一个国家、一个民族对自身历史和文化价值的清晰认知，文化兴则国运兴，文化强则民族强，我们唯有坚定文化自信，才能在世界文化激荡中站稳脚跟，必须把思想和行动统一到习近平总书记的重要讲话上，坚定文化自信，担当文化使命，扎实推进中华民族现代文明和社会主义文化强国建设，奋力谱写新时代中国特色社会主义新篇章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; text-indent: 2.14285em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><section data-role="title" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="128867" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; z-index: 0; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2385,894h56V834h-56l27,30Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2388,890h53v4h-57Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2417,884l24,10V884h-24Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path></svg></section></section><section style="margin: 0px -8px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; z-index: 9; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 15px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(213, 58, 28); border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(255, 217, 82); letter-spacing: 1.5px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">开展集中交流研讨<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"/></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"></strong></span></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2664,894h-56V834h56l-27,30Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2608,890h53l4,4h-57v-4Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2632,884l-24,10V884h24Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.14285em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体;">经济管理学院学生党支部全体党员开展专题交流研讨，学生党支部组织委员王艳萍、学生党员乐柯婧、熊路清参加此次研讨，</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 宋体;">紧紧围绕“深刻把握中华文明的突出性”、“深刻理解‘两个结合’的重大意义”、“更好担负起新的文化使命”这三个方面，结合自身实际情况，就如何有效地推动中华优秀传统文创造性转化化、创新性发展，如何有力地推进中国特色社会主义文化建设，如何建设中华民族现代文明交流讨论。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.14285em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">学生党员表示要坚定地做社会主义核心价值观的坚定信仰者、积极传播者、模范践行者，坚定文化自信、坚持守正创新、秉承开放包容的姿态、赓续历史文脉、谱写当代华章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.14285em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.14285em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">学生党员还表示自己必将学习贯彻习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想，坚持学习中华优秀传统文化，在日常生活中做到内化于心，外化于行。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><section data-role="title" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="128867" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: flex-end;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2385,894h56V834h-56l27,30Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2388,890h53v4h-57Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2417,884l24,10V884h-24Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path></svg></section></section><section style="margin: 0px -8px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; z-index: 9;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 15px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(213, 58, 28); border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(255, 217, 82); letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">公示本月党费缴纳情况</strong></span></p></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.14285em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">党费收缴作为党的基层组织的一项重要工作，是推进党建工作、保证党的活动正常运转的重要环节，在本次主题党日活动上，经济管理学院公示了本月党费缴纳情况，各党员都积极的配合党支部的工作并按时缴纳了党费，履行了党员义务。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><section data-role="title" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="128867" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: flex-end;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2385,894h56V834h-56l27,30Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2388,890h53v4h-57Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2417,884l24,10V884h-24Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path></svg></section></section><section style="margin: 0px -8px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; z-index: 9;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 15px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(213, 58, 28); border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(255, 217, 82); letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; caret-color: red;">讨论预备党员转正</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; caret-color: red;"></strong></span></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 2;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 2.14285em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="text-align: left; text-indent: 29.4736px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">会上，钟宝乐，祝诏谆、陈淑娟3名同志汇报在预备期表现以及需要向党组织说清楚的问题，表明自身坚定不移的入党意愿和全心全意为人民服务的坚定信念。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 2.14285em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">培养人分别介绍预备党员培养考察情况，并先后就预备党员们的思想、行为、工作以及生活等方面的表现发表意见，对其给予肯定，并指出存在的不足。经过党支部大会的认真考察和全面衡量，最后3名同志光荣地成为中共正式党员。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><section data-role="title" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="128867" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: flex-end;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2385,894h56V834h-56l27,30Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2388,890h53v4h-57Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2417,884l24,10V884h-24Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path></svg></section></section><section style="margin: 0px -8px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; z-index: 9;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 15px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(213, 58, 28); border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(255, 217, 82); letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; caret-color: red;">讨论吸收新党员</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; caret-color: red;"></strong></span></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.14285em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: text; text-indent: 2.14285em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">吴本婷、赖如意、程萱3名同志分别汇报在考察期间的表现以及需要向党组织说清楚的问题。</span><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: text; text-indent: 30.0006px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">通过支部大会讨论并以无记名投票的形式表决吸收吴本婷等3位同志为预备党员的决定。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><section data-role="title" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="128867" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: flex-end;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2385,894h56V834h-56l27,30Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2388,890h53v4h-57Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2417,884l24,10V884h-24Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path></svg></section></section><section style="margin: 0px -8px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; z-index: 9;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 15px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(213, 58, 28); border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(255, 217, 82); letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">为新党员佩戴党徽</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></span></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.14285em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">蔡平书记表示，各位党员同志们胸前的党徽无比鲜艳，昭示着大家身上的责任无比重大。希望广大党员，将责任挺于胸前、记在心中、落实到行动上，时刻以一名优秀党员的标准要求自己，处处发挥党员先锋模范作用，为共产主义事业奋斗终身</span><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.14285em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-role="title" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="128867" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: flex-end;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2385,894h56V834h-56l27,30Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2388,890h53v4h-57Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2417,884l24,10V884h-24Z" transform="translate(-2384 -834)"></path></svg></section></section><section style="margin: 0px -8px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; z-index: 9;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 15px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(213, 58, 28); border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(255, 217, 82); letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">重温入党誓词</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></span></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 57 60" style="display: block;"><path style="fill: #c22305;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2664,894h-56V834h56l-27,30Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #ffd952;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2608,890h53l4,4h-57v-4Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path><path style="fill: #941800;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M2632,884l-24,10V884h24Z" transform="translate(-2608 -834)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; line-height: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.14285em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“我志愿加入中国共产党，拥护党的纲领，遵守党的章程，履行党员义务，执行党的决定，严守党的纪律，保守党的秘密，对党忠诚，积极工作，为共产主义奋斗终生，随时准备为党和人名牺牲一切，永不叛党。”每位党员庄严宣誓，向党表明决心，立志要践行初心和使命，为共产主义事业奋斗终身。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; justify-content: center; display: flex; flex-flow: row; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 90%; display: inline-block; width: 609.3px; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto; height: auto; border-style: solid; border-width: 2px; border-color: rgb(222, 78, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left; justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 35px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 606.1px; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240109/1704791854537089694.jpg" title="1704791854537089694.jpg" alt="1.jpg" width="539" height="287" style="width: 539px; height: 287px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.1429em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">此次党员大会为经济管理学院学生党支部增添了新鲜血液、增强了党建力量，同志们纷纷表示要进一步学好软件、报效祖国，以昂扬的姿态迎接新时代的挑战，<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 30.0006px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">为实现中华民族伟大复兴的中国梦而贡献力量。</span></span></p></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>